        "3e776717": {
          "questionId": "3e776717",
          "textAnswers": {
            "answers": [
              {
                "value": "I think an interactive interface to review and verify the assessment would be very helpful, especially if experts from different backgrounds analyzed the documents together. For example, someone with a more technical background could check and validate the sources/recommendations (for example, see the comment left above about https://arxiv.org/pdf/2007.05848). Probably practitioners/users might need more contextualized explanations about some terminologies (e.g. sacreROUGE). I can imagine that in some contexts a technical profile/expert might not be available. I wonder how this tool could help in those cases. If available for limited time, I definitively believe this assessment would accelerate a manual expert review."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
